## 5. Complete File-by-File Analysis

### 5.1 Flutter Frontend — `lib/`

---

#### [main.dart](file:///c:/Users/botch/New_app/MedTek/AI_Flutter_Applications-medtek/medtek/lib/main.dart) — App Entry Point (265 lines)

**What it does:**
- Initializes Flutter bindings, Mapbox access token, and theme preferences
- Sets up `MultiProvider` with 4 providers: [ThemeNotifier](file:///c:/Users/botch/New_app/MedTek/AI_Flutter_Applications-medtek/medtek/lib/main.dart#24-82), `RideProvider`, `LocationProvider`, [SessionService](file:///c:/Users/botch/New_app/MedTek/AI_Flutter_Applications-medtek/medtek/lib/services/session_service.dart#8-124)
- Contains [ThemeNotifier](file:///c:/Users/botch/New_app/MedTek/AI_Flutter_Applications-medtek/medtek/lib/main.dart#24-82) class for dark/light/system theme persistence via `SharedPreferences`
- [EntryGate](file:///c:/Users/botch/New_app/MedTek/AI_Flutter_Applications-medtek/medtek/lib/main.dart#189-195) widget checks session token → calls `/users/me` → routes by role:
  - `doctor` → [DoctorDashboard](file:///c:/Users/botch/New_app/MedTek/AI_Flutter_Applications-medtek/medtek/lib/src/doctor_dashboard.dart#14-20)
  - `lab_assistant` → [LabDashboard](file:///c:/Users/botch/New_app/MedTek/AI_Flutter_Applications-medtek/medtek/lib/src/lab_dashboard.dart#6-12)
  - Default → [PatientDashboard](file:///c:/Users/botch/New_app/MedTek/AI_Flutter_Applications-medtek/medtek/lib/src/patient_dashboard.dart#15-21)
  - No token → [AuthPage](file:///c:/Users/botch/New_app/MedTek/AI_Flutter_Applications-medtek/medtek/lib/src/auth_page.dart#15-21)
- Defines named routes: `/login`, `/home`, `/lab-dashboard`, `/ride-booking`, `/finding-driver`, `/ride-tracking`, `/ride-success`, `/activities`

---

#### Services (`lib/services/`) — 9 files

##### [api_service.dart](file:///c:/Users/botch/New_app/MedTek/AI_Flutter_Applications-medtek/medtek/lib/services/api_service.dart) — Central API Client (1,114 lines)

**Singleton pattern** with Dio HTTP client. Every API call the app makes goes through this file. Key method groups:

| Category | Methods | What They Do |
|---|---|---|
| **Auth** | `login()`, `register()`, `getMe()` | Authentication & session |
| **Profile** | `uploadProfilePicture()`, `updateUserProfile()`, `updateDoctorProfile()`, `getPatientProfile()` | User profile CRUD |
| **Password** | `requestPasswordReset()`, `verifyResetToken()`, `resetPassword()` | 3-step password reset flow |
| **Hospitals** | `getHospitals()`, `searchHospitals()`, `getHospitalById()`, `getNearbyHospitals()`, `getLiveNearbyHospitals()` | Hospital discovery |
| **Doctors** | `getDoctorsForHospital()`, `getDoctorSummary()`, `searchDoctors()`, `getTrendingDoctors()`, `getDoctorReviews()` | Doctor search & info |
| **Appointments** | `createAppointment()`, `getDoctorAppointments()`, `getPendingBookings()`, `updateAppointmentStatus()` | Booking workflow |
| **Medical Reports** | `getMyMedicalReports()`, `createMedicalReport()`, `updateLabTestStatus()`, `completeConsultation()` | Report & lab management |
| **Lab** | `getLabPendingTests()`, `labCollectSample()`, `labCompleteTest()`, `getLabStats()` | Lab assistant operations |
| **Rides** | `createRide()`, `getRide()`, `getMyRides()`, `assignDriver()`, `findNearbyDrivers()`, `updateRideStatus()`, `verifyRidePin()` | Transport management |
| **AI** | `sendChatMessage()`, `sendChatMessageOllama()`, `checkPillSafety()` | AI triage & pill ID |
| **Triage** | `sendTriageResult()`, `saveTriageReport()` | Triage report persistence |
| **Verification** | `getVerificationStatus()`, `submitDoctorVerification()` | Doctor credential verification |
| **Activities** | `getActivities()`, `getPatientActivities()` | Activity timeline |
| **Config** | `loadBaseUrl()`, `updateBaseUrl()` | Dynamic server IP configuration |

##### [session_service.dart](file:///c:/Users/botch/New_app/MedTek/AI_Flutter_Applications-medtek/medtek/lib/services/session_service.dart) — Session Management (124 lines)

- Singleton `ChangeNotifier` for reactive session state
- Persists JWT token + user JSON to `SharedPreferences`
- Methods: `init()`, `saveSession()`, `updateUser()`, `clear()`, `signOut()`, `fetchMe()`, `getToken()`
- Used by Dio interceptor to auto-attach Bearer token to all requests

##### [maps_service.dart](file:///c:/Users/botch/New_app/MedTek/AI_Flutter_Applications-medtek/medtek/lib/services/maps_service.dart) — Maps Utilities (10,618 bytes)

