##### [triage_page.dart](file:///c:/Users/botch/New_app/MedTek/AI_Flutter_Applications-medtek/medtek/lib/src/triage_page.dart) — AI Triage Assistant (1,348 lines)

**The most complex page.** Features:
- **Dual AI Backend**: Switches between Google Gemini and Ollama/OptGPT
- **Multilingual Support**: English, Hindi, Telugu, Tamil, Arabic — affects both AI prompts and speech engines
- **Speech-to-Text**: Records patient symptoms via microphone
- **Text-to-Speech**: Reads AI responses aloud in selected language
- **Chat Interface**: Message bubbles with timestamps, typing indicators
- **Quick Suggestions**: Pre-built symptom shortcuts (headache, fever, etc.)
- **Report Generation**: After conversation, generates a triage report that can be saved
- **Hospital Flow**: After triage → recommend hospital selection → book appointment
- **Language Selector**: Horizontal chip bar to switch languages mid-conversation

