### 5.2 Backend — `backend/`

---

#### [index.js](file:///c:/Users/botch/New_app/MedTek/AI_Flutter_Applications-medtek/medtek/backend/index.js) — Server Entry Point (395 lines)

- Health check endpoint (`/`)
- Middleware stack: Helmet, CORS, rate limiting (production only), JSON body parsing (50MB limit)
- Inline auth routes: `POST /auth/register`, `POST /auth/login`, `GET /users/me`
- Registration creates user + doctor record (if doctor role)
- Login returns JWT (7-day expiry) + hospital data for doctors
- Mounts 14 route modules

#### [db.js](file:///c:/Users/botch/New_app/MedTek/AI_Flutter_Applications-medtek/medtek/backend/db.js) — Database Connection (11 lines)

- PostgreSQL connection pool via `DATABASE_URL` env var
- Optional SSL support via `DB_SSL` env var

#### Routes (`backend/routes/`) — 16 files

##### [ai.js](file:///c:/Users/botch/New_app/MedTek/AI_Flutter_Applications-medtek/medtek/backend/routes/ai.js) — AI Endpoints (358 lines)

Three main endpoints:

| Endpoint | Model | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `POST /ai/chat` | Gemini 2.5 Flash | Medical triage chat with patient profile context |
| `POST /ai/identify-pill` | Gemini 2.5 Flash (Vision) | Pill image analysis + drug interaction checking |
| `POST /ai/chat-ollama` | OptGPT-4:latest (Ollama) | Offline triage with multilingual support |
| `GET /ai/ollama-info` | — | Ollama server & model status |

Key features:
- Retry with exponential backoff (3 retries)
- Personalized system prompts with patient profile
- Pharmacist agent for pill safety (JSON output)
- Multi-language support: EN, HI, TE, TA, AR

##### [lab.js](file:///c:/Users/botch/New_app/MedTek/AI_Flutter_Applications-medtek/medtek/backend/routes/lab.js) — Lab Management (310 lines)

| Endpoint | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `GET /lab/pending-tests` | Get all pending lab tests for assigned hospital |
| `PATCH /lab/test/:reportId/collect-sample` | Mark sample collected |
| `PATCH /lab/test/:reportId/complete` | Mark test done (checks sample first) |
| `GET /lab/stats` | Dashboard stats (pending, collected, completed today) |

Workflow: `pending → sample_collected → done`. When all tests done → report status = `completed`, appointment status = `ready_for_review`.

