## 6. Application Workflows — How Users Use MedTek

### 6.1 Patient Workflow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Open App] --> B{Logged In?}
    B -->|No| C[Register as Patient]
    C --> D[Patient Profile Setup]
    B -->|Yes| E[Patient Dashboard]
    D --> E
    
    E --> F[Browse Trending Doctors]
    E --> G[Search Nearby Hospitals]
    E --> H[AI Triage Chat]
    E --> I[View Medical Reports]
    E --> J[Profile & Settings]
    E --> K[AI Pill Detection]
    
    H --> L[Describe Symptoms]
    L --> M[AI Recommends Specialist]
    M --> N[Select Hospital]
    N --> O[Select Doctor]
    O --> P[Pick Date & Time]
    P --> Q[Confirm Booking]
    Q --> R[Book Ride to Hospital]
    
    G --> S[Hospital Detail Page]
    S --> T[View Doctors at Hospital]
    T --> O
    S --> R
    
    I --> U[View Report Detail]
    U --> V[Track Lab Test Status]
```

**Step-by-step:**

1. **Registration**: Patient creates account → sets up profile (name, age, blood type, allergies, conditions)
2. **Triage**: Opens AI chat → speaks/types symptoms in their language → AI asks clarifying questions → recommends specialist type
3. **Hospital Discovery**: After triage, selects nearby hospital from map view → sees distance, address, available doctors
4. **Appointment Booking**: Picks doctor → selects date/time → confirms → backend creates appointment record
5. **Ride Booking**: Optionally books ride to hospital → sees route on Mapbox map → driver assigned → PIN verified at pickup
6. **Medical Reports**: After consultation, views diagnosis, prescriptions, lab test orders and their real-time status
7. **Pill Detection**: Takes photo of medication → AI identifies pill → checks drug interactions with current meds

---

### 6.2 Doctor Workflow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Register as Doctor] --> B[Hospital Selection]
    B --> C[Verification Screen]
    C --> D[NMC Number Check]
    C --> E[Certificate Upload + OCR]
    C --> F[Selfie + Liveness]
    D & E & F --> G[Verified Status]
    G --> H[Doctor Dashboard]
    
    H --> I[View Pending Bookings]
    I --> J[Accept / Decline]
    J -->|Accept| K[Appointment Confirmed]
    
    H --> L[Today's Patients]
    L --> M[View Patient Detail]
    M --> N[Write Diagnosis]
    M --> O[Write Prescription]
    M --> P[Order Lab Tests]
    P --> Q[Lab Tests Sent to Lab Dashboard]
    
    H --> R[Schedule Management]
    H --> S[Profile Management]
    H --> T[Patient Monitor]
```

1. **Onboarding**: Register → select hospital → complete verification (NMC, certificate OCR, selfie)
2. **Dashboard**: See stats (total patients, today's, pending), recent patient list, pending booking notifications
3. **Booking Management**: Accept/decline incoming patient appointments
4. **Consultation**: Click patient → view history → write diagnosis + prescription + order lab tests
5. **Lab Monitoring**: Track lab test progress in `patient_monitor_page.dart`
6. **Profile**: Update specialization, experience, about, profile picture

---

### 6.3 Lab Assistant Workflow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Register as Lab Assistant] --> B[Assign to Hospital]
    B --> C[Lab Dashboard]
    
    C --> D[View Stats]
    D --> E[Pending Tests Count]
    D --> F[Samples Collected Count]
    D --> G[Completed Today Count]
    
    C --> H[Pending Tests List]
    H --> I[Collect Sample]
    I --> J[Status: sample_collected]
    J --> K[Mark Complete]
    K --> L[Status: done]
    L --> M{All Tests Done?}
    M -->|Yes| N[Report Status = completed]
    N --> O[Appointment = ready_for_review]
    M -->|No| H
```

1. **Assignment**: After registration, assigned to specific hospital
2. **Dashboard**: View pending/collected/completed test counts
3. **Process Tests**: For each test — collect sample → run test → mark complete
4. **Auto-completion**: When all tests for a report are done, report auto-completes and appointment marked as ready for doctor review

---

### 6.4 Ride Booking Workflow

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    A[Patient Selects Hospital] --> B[Book Ride]
    B --> C[Select Pickup/Dropoff]
    C --> D[Ride Created]
    D --> E[Finding Driver...]
    E --> F[Driver Assigned]
    F --> G[Driver En Route]
    G --> H[Driver Arrived]
    H --> I[Verify PIN]
    I --> J[Ride In Progress]
    J --> K[Ride Completed]
    K --> L[Success Page]
```

