## 7. Key Technical Highlights

### AI Integration (Dual-Model Architecture)
- **Gemini 2.5 Flash**: Primary AI for English triage and pill identification (Vision API)
- **OptGPT-4 via Ollama**: Custom-trained local model for multilingual triage (runs on local network)
- Retry with exponential backoff for rate limits (429/503)
- Patient profile context injection into all AI prompts

### Security
- **JWT authentication** with 7-day token expiry
- **bcrypt** password hashing (10 salt rounds)
- **Helmet.js** security headers
- **Rate limiting** in production (100 req/15min)
- **Auth middleware** protects all sensitive routes

### Multilingual Voice Support
- 5 languages: English, Hindi, Telugu, Tamil, Arabic
- Each language has configured: STT locale, TTS language, AI prompt language instruction
- Real-time speech recognition with visual feedback

### Doctor Verification System
- Multi-factor verification: NMC number + Certificate OCR + Selfie liveness
- Points-based scoring stored in JSONB
- Verification badge displayed throughout the app

### Lab Test Lifecycle
- Uses PostgreSQL JSONB (`lab_tests_json`) for flexible test tracking
- 3-stage workflow: `pending → sample_collected → done`
- Atomic updates with automatic report/appointment status propagation

